milestones.description: Klaas-Jan van Noortwijk and Feiko Kloppenburg's 228-run partnership is NED's highest for the 2nd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 74 between Cantrell and Aponso
Morne Karg and Burger's 75-run partnership is NAM's highest for the 1st wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 19 between Burger and Swanepoel
van Schoor and van Rooi's 13-run partnership is NAM's highest for the 9th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 7 between Bjorn Kotze and Deon Kotze
Gerrie Snyman has broken the record for most ducks (3) in ODIs for NAM, going past Riaan Walters's 2
Feiko Kloppenburg has broken the record for most sixes in an innings (4) in ODIs for NED, going past Klaas-Jan van Noortwijk's 2
Klaas-Jan van Noortwijk has broken the record for most runs in boundaries (62) in an innings in ODIs for NED, going past Nolan Clarke's 30
Klaas-Jan van Noortwijk has broken the record for most sixes (6) in ODIs for NED, going past Lefebvre's 3
Tim de Leede has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (13) for NED, going past Bas Zuiderent
Burger has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (6) for NAM, going past Louis Burger
Klaas-Jan van Noortwijk and Feiko Kloppenburg's 228-run partnership is NED's highest for any wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 114 between Bas Zuiderent and Klaas-Jan van Noortwijk
Klaas-Jan van Noortwijk has become the top scorer for NED in ODIs with 322 runs, going past Tim de Leede's 243
Klaas-Jan van Noortwijk has scored 2 fifty-plus scores in ODIs, the most for NED breaking Aponso's record
Klaas-Jan van Noortwijk's 134 is the highest individual score in ODIs (for NED), surpassing Klaas-Jan van Noortwijk's 64

stories.title: Dutch prove to be too strong for brave Namibia
stories.summary: It might not have been of great significance in the overall context of the World Cup, but for Namibia and the Netherlands this match represented the summit of their ambitions to return from South Africa with a victory of which to boast
